#. type: Plain text
#: ../../info/wxmaxima.md:375
msgid ""
"For some common configuration variables _wxMaxima_ offers two ways of "
"configuring:"
msgstr ""
"Pour certaines variables courantes liées à la configuration, _wxMaxima_ "
"propose deux méthodes de configuration :"

